toryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000=
; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom=
-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">the m=
ost important paper in economics</a> is the one about how people sometimes =
give themselves painful electric=C2=A0shocks just because <a href=3D"https:=
//link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32248570.290413/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuc2N=
