3cBba8c370c" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blan=
k" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom=
-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; back=
ground-color: #ccc;">that is an option that=E2=80=99s available to them</a>=
:</p>
<blockquote><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">For 15 minutes, the team left part=
icipants alone in a lab room in which they could push a button and shock th=
emselves if they wanted to. The results were startling: Even though all par=
ticipants had previously stated that they would pay money to avoid being sh=
ocked with electricity, 67% of men and 25% of women chose to inflict it on =
themselves rather than just sit there quietly and think, the team reports o=
nline today in Science.</p></blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">All of human culture is explained by that resu=
lt.=C2=A0Anyway, three questions:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Would you let an artificial-intellige=
nce mogul scan your irises with a chrome=C2=A0orb for purposes of his own, =
if in exchange he gave you $50?</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Wo=
uld you let him do that, if instead of money he gave you some crypto tokens=
 that he made up and that have uncertain value?</li>=09<li style=3D"margin-=
bottom: 5px;">Would you let him do that,=C2=A0<em>without=C2=A0</em>the tok=
ens?</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">When I put it like that it seems like the answ=
er to at least the <em>third=C2=A0</em>question would be =E2=80=9Cno,=E2=80=
=9D but if you have ever met a human=C2=A0you know the answer is =E2=80=9C<=
a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32248570.290413/aHR=
0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9uZXdzL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjMtMDctMjgvdXMtY3J5cH=
RvLWZhbnMtYXJlLWRyYXduLXRvLWFsdG1hbi1zLXdvcmxkY29pbi1vcmItYW5kLXRoZXktcmUtb=
m90LXN1cmUtd2h5P2NtcGlkPUJCRDA3MzEyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09ZW1haWwm=
dXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDczMSZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249bW9uZXl=
